bmdca
------------------------------------------
Boltzmann-machine Direct Coupling Analysis

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libgomp1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/ranganathanlab/bmDCA

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/ranganathanlab/bmDCA/archive/refs/tags/v0.8.13.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bmdca-0.8.13-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bmdca-0.8.13-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bmdca-0.8.13-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bmdca-0.8.13-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(bmdca)
  /usr/bin/arma2ascii.exe
  /usr/bin/bmdca.exe
  /usr/bin/bmdca_sample.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/bmdca.README
  /usr/share/doc/bmdca/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/bmdca/README.md

